embeds.title: not yet a member of the club? join us to join our events~
embeds.description:
We're a club dedicated to learning about and appreciating coffee in all its forms. We hold meet-ups where you can catch up with fellow enthusiasts and enjoy the highest-quality brews on campus!
The link to our homepage can be found at >>@https://umsu.unimelb.edu.au/buddy-up/clubs/clubs-listing/join/cafe/
